OL,3,CHundreds face losing their homes after
OL,4,Cflats declared unsafe
OL,6,FITV News' Emma Sweeney has been
OL,7,Fspeaking to those affected by the
OL,8,Fclosure of more than 160 homes.
OL,10,FHundreds of people face being forced
OL,11,Fout of their homes after the fire
OL,12,Fservice declared two tower blocks
OL,13,Funsafe.
OL,15,FThe 160 households at Willow Rise and
OL,16,FBeech Rise at Kirkby in Merseyside
OL,17,Fhave been told they will have to leave
OL,18,Fwithin weeks.
