OL,6,FMerseyside Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fsays it has no choice but to serve a
OL,8,Fprohibition notice.
OL,10,FThe long running wrangle comes after
OL,11,Fyears of problems at the flats with
OL,12,Fresidents complaining of mould, broken
OL,13,Flifts and leaks.
OL,15,FKnowsley Council - which does not own
OL,16,For manage them - says responsibility
OL,17,Fhas changed several times since 2017
OL,18,Fwith different management agents being
OL,19,Fappointed but only remaining involved
OL,20,Ffor short periods.
