OL,6,FThe latest company to take on that
OL,7,Frole two years ago claimed it tried to
OL,8,Fmake improvements but inherited a
OL,9,Fdevelopment that had suffered from
OL,10,Fyears of neglect.
OL,12,FNow MFRS says it's not safe for people
OL,13,Fto live there because "essential
OL,14,Frepairs" haven't been carried out.
OL,16,FThey will have to move out as soon as
OL,17,Fa temporary safety measure is
OL,18,Fwithdrawn.
