OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We understand
OL,7,Fthat this is disruptive and unpleasant
OL,8,Ffor residents, however all other
OL,9,Foptions have been exhausted and the
OL,10,Fsafety of residents is of paramount
OL,11,Fimportance. "
OL,13,FChristopher Penfold-Ivany, 53, lives
OL,14,Fin Willow Rise and is having treatment
OL,15,Ffor cancer.
