OL,6,F"Right now, I don't know where I'm
OL,7,Fgoing to live, but before that, I
OL,8,Fdon't know how I'm going to move ` how
OL,9,Fcan anyone move because the lifts
OL,10,Fdon't work and there's lots of
OL,11,Fpeople's belongings here such as
OL,12,Ffurniture," he said.
OL,14,F"The thought of moving is very very
OL,15,Fstressful and could have a serious
OL,16,Fimpact on people's health. We've been
OL,17,Fplunged into uncertainty and we're all
OL,18,Feffectively being made homeless."
